### TITLE ###
Can print colored text
### INPUT ###
print(red("Alice"))
print(blue("Bob"))
print(yellow("Charlie"))
print(yellow(2))
print(blue([true, "hi", 10]))
### ARGS ###
--color=always
### STDOUT ###
[31mAlice[0m
[34mBob[0m
[33mCharlie[0m
[33m2[0m
[34m[ true, "hi", 10 ][0m

### TITLE ###
